{"tid":1569572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極醜惡]第二銀河香港聯盟被官方惡意消滅","createTime":"2019-09-14T16:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T06:53:10.000Z","uid":278753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84b5a7bb73c820043962fe730426a747f512ad18","tid":1569572,"uid":278753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"遊戲官方擅自刪改遊戲進程，剷除1100位香港玩家於遊戲內加入的整個星盟！<br />\n就連玩遊戲都要欺壓香港人!<br />\n<br />\nLiberty聯盟旗下有8隊香港軍團，逾1100名活躍香港玩家。<br />\n本來今晚10時30分將進行一場對NPC的大型團戰，數百玩家都已會合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1bpAAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1bpAAs.png&h=20292c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在大約10時10分，各軍團團長帳戶突然相繼斷線<br />\n更被宣稱帳戶已被&quot;託管&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPwH6wW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPwH6wW.jpg&h=0d440100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其後疑似官方人員通過團長帳戶將所有成員踢出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WyCVqD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WyCVqD.jpg&h=e7104280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uo3CVq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuo3CVq2.jpg&h=aad68818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在11點27分，各個軍團都被官方刪除<br />\n<br />\n聯盟甚至刻意在遊戲中避談政治，對於此等幼稚行為表達強烈不滿，並對無故政治打壓表示遺憾。"},{"pid":"48852f937f71e249eb0d768315b7629018bc41c3","tid":1569572,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:11:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7694fa6d92f5f51768343b4b24593cd0317036f4","tid":1569572,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-